HEADWORD: Regretful
<hw>Re*gret"ful</hw> <pr>(-f?l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of regret;
indulging in regrets; repining.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Re*gret"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

